snippet.title: Bathhouse Creatures | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Bathhouse Creatures is a casual and cozy time management game about building up an old bathhouse, keeping animal guests happy, and watching your bathhouse grow to be the best it can be! 🐥♨️💖

Wishlist now on Steam!
